(544,	1,	'2015-03-09 06:57:38',	'2015-03-09 06:57:38',	'As an Army medic, Luke had seen enough heart ache to fill a lifetime. After being injured on an overseas deployment, Luke returned to Australia to see the rest of his life fall apart. During a painful recovery Luke met Jess through an online dating service. After just a few dates it was clear that she had reignited his soul.  \r\nA little over 3 years after meeting they married in the beautiful rainforest at Mount Keira, near Wollongong.  \r\n\r\nJessica arrived with her mother in a 1940\'s dark silver Buick and her bridesmaids followed in white Buicks. Harry from Cool Classic Cars ensured the bridal party was well cared for and always went the extra mile to accommodate the bridal couple.',	'Mount Kiera',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'518-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-03-09 06:57:38',	'2015-03-09 06:57:38',	'',	518,	'http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/518-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
