(668,	1,	'2015-03-26 06:30:01',	'2015-03-26 06:30:01',	'[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_gallery images=\"65,64\" type=\"flexslider_slide\" grid_style=\"circle\" img_size=\"full\" columns=\"col3\" onclick=\"link_image\" interval=\"10\" show_bullets=\"true\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Army Nursing Officer turned wedding photographer\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]I’m Samantha Ohlsen and I’m a Sydney-based photographer specialising in wedding and portrait photography services to the greater Sydney area.\r\n\r\nBefore becoming a professional wedding photographer I spent many years working as an Army Nursing Officer in war-torn areas, like Afghanistan, where I helped people through the worse days of their lives. I found the work incredibly rewarding but I was also profoundly affected by the sadness and tragedy of what I saw.\r\n\r\nWhen I left those areas I wanted to immerse myself in the complete opposite of what I had experienced, so I set about capturing the gentle and beautiful side of life and surrounding myself in the joy of others, through photography.\r\n\r\nMy love affair with the camera began as a hobby but after I shot my first wedding - I was hooked. There’s something so magical about spending an entire day with a bride and groom on their wedding day.\r\n\r\nAnd I also found my background lends itself beautifully to wedding photography:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I’m organised, meticulous and leave nothing to chance so you can relax and be confident knowing that one of the most important days of your life is in capable hands.</li>\r\n	<li>Working with people of all ages and backgrounds has given me an exceptional ability to put anyone at ease, whatever the situation. When you are comfortable you are present in the moment, which is perfect for lovely, natural shots.</li>\r\n	<li>My well-developed sense of intuition and keen observation skills mean I am attuned to seeing and feeling what’s going on around me. This enables me to shoot from the heart and not miss those precious ‘real’, intimate and often fleeting moments.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMy aim is to make your special day joyful and stress-free and I strive to create a highly personalised experience, both before and after your wedding day.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"What matters to me\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]Telling your story is what matters to me. When you are relaxed and enjoying your day it enables me to capture those beautiful moments that naturally occur. Making sure you are relaxed is primary part of my support role as your Wedding Photographer.  I love using vibrant colours, textures and reflections as part of the storytelling process, to enhance the beauty of you too and the surroundings. Black and white images will be utilised to perfectly capture mood.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"What I specialize in\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]I specialise in classic timeless stories, ensuring your special day is documented with images to last a lifetime. I am passionate about making you look as good as you feel for those special moments in your life. I value reliability, honesty, trust, professionalism and timeliness. I have a long history within the military so I understand the planning that goes into special days such as your wedding and understand what it takes to maintain a high level of professionalism even under the most stressful of times.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"What you can expect\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]You can expect me to be organised and capable of meeting deadlines and keeping to any schedule that you have set for your special day. I am a specialist of attention to detail and will have plans in place should the weather not be ideal. With my exceptional attention to detail I can help guide you to planning a stress free wedding day. This means that you can concentrate on your special day and leave any worries with me.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][uxb_heading text=\"Words Form Client\" type=\"h3\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][uxb_testimonials id_list=\"75,49,76\" type=\"full-width\" interval=\"10\" orderby=\"ID\" order=\"DESC\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_cta_button uxb_color_line=\"none\" display_button=\"true\" position=\"cta_align_right\" title=\"CONTACT SAMANTHA today\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" el_class=\"about-contact-form\" href=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/contact/\"]Sounds like we might click?\r\n\r\nI\'d love to chat or meet with to discuss your wedding[/vc_cta_button][/vc_column][/vc_row]',	'About',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'61-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-03-26 06:30:01',	'2015-03-26 06:30:01',	'',	61,	'http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/61-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
