(140,	75,	'uxbarn_testimonial_text',	'Samantha clearly went over and above what could be expected from other photographers. She did her homework to ensure any hiccups were dealt with seamlessly. Samantha is empathetic, professional and organized. This meant that on the day not only did our day run better, it also put us in the right frame of mind to capture the best images. \r\n\r\nPrior to the event Sam\'s contributions, thoughts and ideas gave us the scope to capture the day in a way that we never considered, she really helped us express ourselves in a lasting record of our wedding.\r\n'),
