(144,	76,	'uxbarn_testimonial_text',	'Before working with Samantha I was hesitant due to the cost and not having worked with Samantha before. We had such a wonderful week with family and friends on Lord Howe and we thank Samantha so much for capturing what it felt like on the day to marry my best friend! The photos are excellent, they were far better than we could have dreamed, some are truly breathtaking and we received many more than we expected.'),
