(61,	1,	'2015-03-03 09:23:38',	'2015-03-03 09:23:38',	'[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_gallery images=\"65,64\" type=\"flexslider_slide\" grid_style=\"circle\" img_size=\"full\" columns=\"col3\" onclick=\"link_image\" interval=\"10\" show_bullets=\"true\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Army Nursing Officer turned wedding photographer\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]I’m Samantha Ohlsen and I’m a Sydney-based photographer specialising in wedding and portrait photography services to the greater Sydney area.\r\n\r\nBefore becoming a professional wedding photographer I spent many years working as an Army Nursing Officer in war-torn areas, like Afghanistan, where I helped people through the worse days of their lives. I found the work incredibly rewarding but I was also profoundly affected by the sadness and tragedy of what I saw.\r\n\r\nWhen I left those areas I wanted to immerse myself in the complete opposite of what I had experienced, so I set about capturing the gentle and beautiful side of life and surrounding myself in the joy of others, through photography.\r\n\r\nMy love affair with the camera began as a hobby but after I shot my first wedding - I was hooked. There’s something so magical about spending an entire day with a bride and groom on their wedding day.\r\n\r\nAnd I also found my background lends itself beautifully to wedding photography:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I’m organised, meticulous and leave nothing to chance so you can relax and be confident knowing that one of the most important days of your life is in capable hands.</li>\r\n	<li>Working with people of all ages and backgrounds has given me an exceptional ability to put anyone at ease, whatever the situation. When you are comfortable you are present in the moment, which is perfect for lovely, natural shots.</li>\r\n	<li>My well-developed sense of intuition and keen observation skills mean I am attuned to seeing and feeling what’s going on around me. This enables me to shoot from the heart and not miss those precious ‘real’, intimate and often fleeting moments.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMy aim is to make your special day joyful and stress-free and I strive to create a highly personalised experience, both before and after your wedding day.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"A few more facts\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]I’m a die-hard coffee lover. I simply can’t get by without great coffee. When I lived in New York I walked 14 blocks each morning to kick off the day with the perfect brew. Now that’s love. My other loves, besides photography, are travelling, scuba diving, and enjoying amazing food and wine from all over the world. My passion for travel has also led me into the specialised field of destination wedding photography. Ask me about Lord Howe – it’s amazing. I also love craft beers and sampling pale ales at microbreweries.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"A strong set of values\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]I value reliability, honesty, trust, and timeliness. I understand the planning involved in special days, such as your wedding, and you can expect a high level of professionalism from me, even under the most stressful of circumstances.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Plenty of passion\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]I’m passionate about making you look as good as you feel. As a woman, I understand how important it is that I highlight your best features - your beautiful dress, your hair and makeup and that beautiful beaming smile that radiates because you’re marrying your soul mate. I use vibrant colours, textures and reflections, as well as black and white images, to tell your unique story and create beautiful timeless imagery that you will treasure always.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][uxb_heading text=\"Words Form Client\" type=\"h3\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][uxb_testimonials id_list=\"75,49,76\" type=\"full-width\" interval=\"10\" orderby=\"ID\" order=\"DESC\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_cta_button uxb_color_line=\"none\" display_button=\"true\" position=\"cta_align_right\" title=\"CONTACT SAMANTHA today\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" el_class=\"about-contact-form\" href=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/contact/\"]Sounds like we might click?\r\n\r\nI\'d love to chat or meet with to discuss your wedding[/vc_cta_button][/vc_column][/vc_row]',	'About',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'about',	'',	'',	'2015-03-30 06:38:13',	'2015-03-30 06:38:13',	'',	0,	'http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/?page_id=61',	8,	'page',	'',	0),
