k\" type=\"h3\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]A First Look can add a touch of magic to your wedding day. A First Look is when a bride and groom see each other before the wedding ceremony.\r\n\r\nNormally considered a bit ‘Taboo’ to see your bride before the ceremony, this is fast becoming the most loved moment of a couple’s day. You met up alone, away from your wedding party, and it is a moment shared by just the two of you, it is relaxing and very romantic. Another great benefit is that the ceremony is much more relaxed.[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"27\" img_size=\"full\" image_position=\"normal-align-left\" has_link=\"false\" link_type=\"normal\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"40\" img_size=\"full\" image_position=\"normal-align-left\" has_link=\"false\" link_type=\"normal\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][uxb_heading text=\"Words From Clients\" type=\"h3\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][uxb_testimonials id_list=\"44,49,48\" type=\"full-width\" interval=\"10\" orderby=\"ID\" order=\"ASC\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][uxb_heading text=\"Recent Blog Posts and Weddings\" type=\"h3\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]',	'Home',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'9-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-03-03 11:01:24',	'2015-03-03 11:01:24',	'',	9,	'http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/9-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
