(104,	1,	'2015-03-04 03:19:20',	'2015-03-04 03:19:20',	'[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_gallery images=\"65,64\" type=\"flexslider_slide\" grid_style=\"circle\" img_size=\"full\" columns=\"col3\" onclick=\"link_image\" interval=\"10\" show_bullets=\"true\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Army Nurse Commander turned Wedding Photographer\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]I am a Sydney based photographer offering wedding and portrait photography services to the greater Sydney area and beyond. Destination weddings, in particular Lord Howe Island are well catered. I specialise in attention to detail to minimise the stress for your special day.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"What matters to me\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]Telling your story is what matters to me. When you are relaxed and enjoying your day it enables me to capture those beautiful moments that naturally occur. Making sure you are relaxed is primary part of my support role as your Wedding Photographer.  I love using vibrant colours, textures and reflections as part of the storytelling process, to enhance the beauty of you too and the surroundings. Black and white images will be utilised to perfectly capture mood.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"What I specialize in\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]I specialise in classic timeless stories, ensuring your special day is documented with images to last a lifetime. I am passionate about making you look as good as you feel for those special moments in your life. I value reliability, honesty, trust, professionalism and timeliness. I have a long history within the military so I understand the planning that goes into special days such as your wedding and understand what it takes to maintain a high level of professionalism even under the most stressful of times.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"What you can expect\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]You can expect me to be organised and capable of meeting deadlines and keeping to any schedule that you have set for your special day. I am a specialist of attention to detail and will have plans in place should the weather not be ideal. With my exceptional attention to detail I can help guide you to planning a stress free wedding day. This means that you can concentrate on your special day and leave any worries with me.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][uxb_heading text=\"Words Form Client\" type=\"h3\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][uxb_testimonials id_list=\"75,49,76\" type=\"full-width\" interval=\"10\" orderby=\"ID\" order=\"DESC\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][vc_cta_button uxb_color_line=\"none\" display_button=\"true\" position=\"cta_align_right\" title=\"CONTACT SAMANTHA\r\ntoday\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" el_class=\"about-contact-form\"]Sounds like we might click?\r\n\r\nI\'d love to chat or meet with to discuss your wedding[/vc_cta_button][/vc_column][/vc_row]',	'About',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'61-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-03-04 03:19:20',	'2015-03-04 03:19:20',	'',	61,	'http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/61-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(106,	1,	'2015-03-04 03:25:43',	'2015-03-04 03:25:43',	'[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_gallery images=\"696,695,697\" type=\"flexslider_slide\" grid_style=\"circle\" img_size=\"full\" columns=\"col3\" onclick=\"link_image\" interval=\"10\" show_bullets=\"true\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][uxb_heading text=\"Practice makes perfect\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\"][vc_column_text]An engagement session is a great way to do dry run for the big day. It allows us to get to know each other a little better and it helps you feel more comfortable in front of a camera.\r\n\r\nYou’ll also get some lovely, relaxed photos of the two of you that you can add to your wedding album or use for ‘save the date’ cards and invitations.\r\n\r\nThe engagement session can happen up to a month before the wedding and be easily added to one my wedding photography packages.\r\n\r\nGet in touch for a chat or to book your engagement session.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"Contact Samantha today\" href=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/contact/\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_heading text=\"TAKE A CLOSER LOOK AT A SELECTION OF ENGAGEMENTS\" type=\"h1\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\" alignment=\"h-center\"][vc_separator color=\"grey\" style=\"double\"][vc_empty_space height=\"32px\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Melissa and James\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\" alignment=\"h-center\"][vc_single_image image=\"115\" img_size=\"full\" image_position=\"normal-align-left\" has_link=\"true\" link_type=\"normal\" img_link=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/portfolio/melissa-james/\"][vc_column_text]When Melissa and James were married four years ago they experienced what every bride and groom dreads - the wedding photographer was a no show.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"See More\" href=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/portfolio/melissa-james/\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" uxb_icon=\" icon-caret-right\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Luke and Jess\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\" alignment=\"h-center\"][vc_single_image image=\"114\" img_size=\"full\" image_position=\"normal-align-left\" has_link=\"true\" link_type=\"normal\" img_link=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/portfolio/luke-jess/\"][vc_column_text]As an Army medic, Luke had seen enough heart ache to fill a lifetime. After being injured on an overseas deployment, Luke returned to Australia to see the rest of his life fall apart.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"See More\" href=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/portfolio/luke-jess/\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" uxb_icon=\" icon-caret-right\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Bill and Joanne\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"true\" icon_size=\"16\" alignment=\"h-center\"][vc_single_image image=\"118\" img_size=\"full\" image_position=\"normal-align-left\" has_link=\"true\" link_type=\"normal\" img_link=\"#\"][vc_column_text]As an Army medic, Luke had seen enough heart ache to fill a lifetime. After being injured on an overseas deployment, Luke returned to Australia to see the rest of his life fall apart.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"See More\" href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" uxb_icon=\" icon-caret-right\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][uxb_divider style=\"special\"][uxb_testimonials id_list=\"44,75,49\" type=\"full-width\" interval=\"10\" orderby=\"ID\" order=\"ASC\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_cta_button uxb_color_line=\"none\" display_button=\"true\" position=\"cta_align_right\" title=\"CONTACT SAMANTHA today\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" el_class=\"about-contact-form\" href=\"htt