(183,	1,	'2015-03-04 07:00:19',	'2015-03-04 07:00:19',	'[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Engagements\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\" alignment=\"h-center\"][vc_single_image image=\"15\" img_size=\"full\" image_position=\"normal-align-left\" has_link=\"true\" link_type=\"normal\" img_link=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/engagement/\"][vc_column_text]A couple’s photo shoot is the perfect opportunity for you to learn to relax in front of the camera[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"See More\" href=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/engagement/\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" uxb_icon=\" icon-caret-right\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Pre-Weddings\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\" alignment=\"h-center\"][vc_single_image image=\"13\" img_size=\"full\" image_position=\"normal-align-left\" has_link=\"true\" link_type=\"normal\" img_link=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/pre-wedding/\"][vc_column_text]Hair, makeup and an amazing gown. What else to do than add an amazing set of photographs of you and your fiancé[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"See More\" href=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/pre-wedding/\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" uxb_icon=\" icon-caret-right\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][uxb_heading text=\"Weddings\" type=\"h2\" has_line=\"false\" icon_size=\"16\" alignment=\"h-center\"][vc_single_image image=\"14\" img_size=\"full\" image_position=\"normal-align-left\" has_link=\"true\" link_type=\"normal\" img_link=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/wedding/\"][vc_column_text]Where I tell your romantic story and record the fun and emotion of the day. For some extra magic, why not add a First Look.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title=\"See More\" href=\"http://samantha.bizcatalyst.com.au/wedding/\" target=\"_self\" size=\"wpb_regularsize\" uxb_icon=\" icon-caret-right\"